<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">5倍速算法，一个数乘以5，可将这个数折半后扩大10倍，即为所求之积。其口诀是：5乘以某数先折半，尾数逢偶把零添。可用公式</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">a×5=a÷2×10</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">136×5=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 136×5</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=136÷2×10</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=68×10</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=680</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>